name: Watched Cook's Country from America's Test Kitchen 11x09 "Reimagining Italian American Classics"
Cook's Country from America's Test Kitchen 11x09 "Reimagining Italian American Classics"

item.value: Cook's Country from America's Test Kitchen 11x09 "Reimagining Italian American Classics"

content.html:
Test cook Bryan Roof makes host Julia Collin Davison a regional favorite — Detroit-style pizza. Then, equipment expert Adam Ried reviews rasp-style graters. And finally, test cook Ashley Moore makes host Bridget Lancaster an updated version of a classic dish — fettuccine with butter and cheese.

Watched on Trakt
